    {
        "content": "<p>I think there are some missing theorems about measurable functions wrt the <code>supr</code> measurable space though</p>",
        "id": 213817353,
        "sender_full_name": "Mario Carneiro",
        "timestamp": 1603127861
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If this is true then the proofs of these missing theorems should be verbatim copy of the corresponding topological theorems.</p>",
